  "texts": [
    "The average score obtained was 6.95/15 points (M = 6.95, SD = 3.84).",
    "To examine the impact of previous knowledge on students' AI interaction profiles in 1st activity session, a one-way ANOVA was conducted.",
    "There were 127 participants both taking previous knowledge test and participating the 1st activity session.",
    "The mean test scores for each profile types were as AI-Reliant Code Generators (M = 5.5, SD = 3.49), AI-Reliant Code Generator & Refiners (M = 6.0, SD = 2.92), AI-Assisted Code Refiners (M = 8.35, SD = 3.22), AI-Independent Coders (M = 7.65, SD = 4.69), and AI-Collaborative Coders (M = 7.29, SD = 4.10).",
    "A one-way ANOVA revealed that there is a significant effect of previous knowledge on AI interaction profiles of 1st activity session [F (4, 122) = 3.35, p =.012, η² = 0.099]."
  ],
